description: Bob’s Fish Fry is trucking the best flavors found around the lakes of Texas throughout the streets of Tennessee. Just one bite of any of Bob’s fresh hot fried fish delights will transport your palate to those simple feel-good Southern summer times. Come out and fill up on some mighty scrumptious Fish & Chips, Fish Tacos, Hush Puppies, French Fries, Shrimp Gumbo, and so much more. For fantastic food and folksy vibes, stop on by Bob’s Fish Fry!
name: Bob's Fish Fry
